      "description": "Each creature in the 30-foot Cone that fails the Wisdom save drops what it is holding and is Frightened for up to 1 minute with concentration. While Frightened, it takes the Dash action and moves away by the safest route each turn if it can, and it repeats the Wisdom save only after ending a turn without line of sight to you, ending the spell on itself on a success.",
