    "prompt": "Prompt Wisdom saves for creatures in the 30-foot Cone; on a failure, make the target drop what it is holding, apply Frightened, force safest-route Dash movement away from the caster when possible, and offer the repeat Wisdom save only after the target ends a turn without line of sight to the caster.",
    "playerInputRequired": true
